{"tid":2175214,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[伴咖啡良物][簡易] 意式餅乾biscotti/cantuccini","createTime":"2020-08-26T10:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-02T05:45:32.000Z","uid":340796,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"609ffba20e231aaa34059df67bbf2ac026ac68ce","tid":2175214,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:54:56.000Z","msg":"好易整, 冇牛油<br />\n唯一的液體係蛋, 所以成品好有舊式港式雞蛋餅嘅味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n整咗好傳統嘅杏仁味<br />\n蛋+自發粉+糖+雲呢嗱, 加入杏仁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J5Tmb22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ5Tmb22.jpg&h=6a6615db&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UR6u5ok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUR6u5ok.jpg&h=6b2045a3&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n撈到成團, 造型<br />\n掃蛋漿就可以入爐<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rL1nFWs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrL1nFWs.jpg&h=53eee11e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cmV0WC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cmV0WC.jpg&h=ce14722f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n攤凍就可以切厚片<span class=\"medium\">(切切吓發現唔夠熟)</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 反正要焗兩次<br />\n入爐焗第二次直到每塊都脆口, 中途要翻一翻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/78EHFWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F78EHFWM.jpg&h=359bd0c0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RNaPkXn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRNaPkXn.jpg&h=3a1575d0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qKqoqo3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqKqoqo3.jpg&h=954a93cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新鮮出爐送黑咖啡真係好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n尋日整蔓越莓橙味<br />\n刨橙皮落糖度, 再用手搓出橙油<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAGCuUe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAGCuUe.jpg&h=99777a5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctTUw3x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctTUw3x.jpg&h=9547f0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成碗糖會變橙色<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d68YegX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd68YegX.jpg&h=ff8aee69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mq3QPQj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmq3QPQj.jpg&h=4e6a67b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇睇火, 燶咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vaesR3F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvaesR3F.jpg&h=06e80112&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n早兩日整咗KFC 鬆餅, 又係好易整<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hTBV0Xd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhTBV0Xd.jpg&h=9a82893f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"662cb361b816612514171d5e7661a34b7ee785e0","tid":2175214,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:55:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcdcc336b2b5dc69c858174817bf4e3c327053a9","tid":2175214,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:55:32.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e58ff5093829728d56a2042dd60b6ae7c3e717bf","tid":2175214,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"牙燕好勁"},{"pid":"5ec2f148b4b530367ef977850419ab8f0c272b76","tid":2175214,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:56:13.000Z","msg":"個餅乾我未食過<br />\n鬆餅同kfc一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65163ad87760dd3f2c798b0341d1dacdbdacce5","tid":2175214,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"隔住moon都覺得好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786795f70377db1c94a1588ca30e647716cd5a72","tid":2175214,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ec2f148b4b530367ef977850419ab8f0c272b76","tid":2175214,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:56:13.000Z","msg":"個餅乾我未食過<br />\n鬆餅同kfc一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我知starbucks 有<br />\n又貴, 咁易整自己整"},{"pid":"203ae8bcfe09dc0e073783b339ad3fafb2db7013","tid":2175214,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"中意紅莓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee59edeac61abf7b3fed7f47bebf0060e7b4ccf7","tid":2175214,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0df27efc6b6c7c99a5b2378e29ecf799a61c3c04","tid":2175214,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d65163ad87760dd3f2c798b0341d1dacdbdacce5","tid":2175214,"uid":299794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:56:14.000Z","msg":"隔住moon都覺得好香<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:59:03.000Z","msg":"真, 好少話自己整野好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個不得了, 啱啱食咗幾塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n配無糖豆漿可以做早餐"},{"pid":"17c8eeecb484e8d5d527cfcf8b4075badb0052da","tid":2175214,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee59edeac61abf7b3fed7f47bebf0060e7b4ccf7","tid":2175214,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:58:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"yes yes 應該係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過佢係搽咗蜜糖係面"},{"pid":"e9ecaac58b6ab0671e43e65d3e1e49cd2422e4d0","tid":2175214,"uid":258109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:59:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"106e079ff4d0c0e0df11beadcd4dcbb8ac7ac0d7","tid":2175214,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T11:00:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d6ed2c211ba5d22e17fd6734b101698d7913807","tid":2175214,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"203ae8bcfe09dc0e073783b339ad3fafb2db7013","tid":2175214,"uid":272819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"中意紅莓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"好食<br />\n遲啲整creamcheese bagel<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1df39b836db31f39d0cae370d81abd6fdde3c9","tid":2175214,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e58ff5093829728d56a2042dd60b6ae7c3e717bf","tid":2175214,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"牙燕